<item>
            <title>[SOLR-698] SpellCheckComponent should use the queryString set in the ResponseBuilder</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-698</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;SpellCheckComponent should check if a previous component has set the queryString property on ResponseBuilder before using the &quot;q&quot; parameter.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This will allow it to be used with query components besides QueryComponent.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12402330">SOLR-698</key>
            <summary>SpellCheckComponent should use the queryString set in the ResponseBuilder</summary>
